A little bit about myself...

My name is Kenneth Petiote and I am a full-time IT Professional.

My knack for learning about technology has lead me to pursuit a certification in Full Stack Web Development. As an aspiring Developer, I enrolled and completed an extensive Web Development Program at Rutgers's Coding Bootcamp.

During the program I've acquired skills in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, MySQL, Node.JS, React.js, and Third Party API's. I look forward to branching into software developing as my new career path. Possessing a solid work ethic, excellent communication skills, I am a strong team player who can work within any department as well as independently.

Aside from coding, I love photography, gaming, and working out.

I own a side business as an event photographer.
